*Suprotno* sebi, on je svojim postupcima izazvao problem. (Contrary to himself, he caused a problem with his actions.)

Njegovo ponašanje se potpuno razlikovalo od onoga što je prethodno radio, u potpunom *suprotnom* smeru. (His behavior was completely different from what he had done before, in a completely opposite direction.)

Ona odlučuje da čini ono *suprotno* od onoga što je njen otac preporučio. (She decides to do the opposite of what her father had recommended.)

U prvom trenutku on je bio ubeđen da je ona zaključila pogrešan zaključak, ali se kasnije ispostavilo da je on bio *suprotan*. (At first he was convinced that she had drawn the wrong conclusion, but it later turned out to be the opposite.)

Ona je svojim postupcima dokazala da je *suprotno* svima njihovim očekivanjima. (She proved with her actions that it was opposite to all of their expectations.)